6. Livox SDK
https://github.com/Livox-SDK/

在BALM项目的根目录打开终端,在此终端下source livox_ros_driver的bash文件,如source ~/xxx/livox_ros_driver/devel/setup.bash,然后再catkin_make即可顺利编译BALM

